\[v \frac{dv}{dr} 
= - \frac{a^2}{\rho} \frac{d\rho}{dr} + \frac{P_\mathrm{gas}}{P_\mathrm{rad}} \frac{\kappa}{4c} \frac{L_\mathrm{rad}}{4\pi r^2} + \frac{\kappa L_\mathrm{rad}}{4\pi c r^2} - \frac{GM_r}{r^2} 
= - \frac{a^2}{\rho} \frac{d\rho}{dr} + \frac{\kappa L_\mahtrm{rad}}{4\pi c r^2} \left( 1 + \frac{P_\mathrm{gas}}{P_\mathrm{rad}}\right) - \frac{GM_r}{r^2} 
= - \frac{a^2}{\rho} \frac{d\rho}{dr} - \frac{GM_r}{r} (1-\Gamma_\mathrm{rad}) \tag{5}\]

<p>ãŒå¾—ã‚‰ã‚Œã¾ã™ã€‚
